schools.name: Edward E. Drew Jr. Middle School

data.description: Do you need more space? Do you like great HOA amenities? Do you wish you lived in a place with sidewalks to stroll and streetlights to light your path? Do you like a home with upgrades? Well, we have it for you … all bundled together in our newest Leeland Station listing! This IMMACULATE home spans 3 finished levels and includes over 4,200 FINISHED SF! This stunner features 5 BD, 3.5 BA, a family room with a floor-to-ceiling stone front gas fireplace, a gourmet kitchen with a sky-lit sunroom just off of it, an office, a formal living room, a formal dining room, a HUGE rec room with a custom wet bar, a bonus/flex room that could be used for a 6th BD (NTC) or workout room or whatever you like, a stamped concrete patio with a view of the trees, a cozy front porch, etc.. the list just keeps going. This home also showcases upgrades like granite countertops, crown molding, chair rail, a soaking tub, 1-year old stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, cathedral ceiling, walk-in closets, gorgeous landscaping, an invisible fence, and more. Plus, the community amenities include a pool, tot lots, walking trails, tennis courts, a clubhouse, and more. Prepare to have your heart stolen when you see this beauty in person!
